Title: Fuzzy Legs
Description:
We have received a request for "Fuzzy Legs" for tailoring...

Don't look at me, I don't make the requests, I just pass them on. I imagine the legs of tarantulas would fulfill this request.
ObjectivesText: Gather 20 Fuzzy Legs from the tarantulas of the Dragon Isles for Gnoklin Quirkcoil of the Dragonscale Expedition.
